                            <comment id="13643579" author="davsclaus" created="Sat, 27 Apr 2013 07:27:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is likely IBM JDK/JVM issue as the option in Camel doesn&apos;t do something different really.&lt;br/&gt;
